commitResults.messageTitle: Remove the address field from Person

commitResults.messageBody:
Duplicate Name class and rename accordingly.

Duplicate NameTest class and rename accordingly.

Create new package for ingredients.

Implement IngredientQuantity class by storing the string describing
the quantity of an ingredient.

Implement the Ingredient class as a composition of an IngredientName
and an IngredientQuantity.

Add an empty IngredientTest class.
Remove extra space.

Add Apache Commons Math 3.6.2 to gradle dependencies.

Create `MixedFraction` class that extends from the Apache Commons
Math `Fraction` class.

Add method to parse a `MixedFraction` from a `String`.

Add tests for `MixedFraction`.

Implement `IngredientQuantity` as a value and an optional unit,
instead of a `String`.

Update validation regex to support inputs that can be parsed into
a value and a unit.

Add support for values as Integer, Double, and MixedFraction.

Add tests for `IngredientQuantity` to test the new validation
regex.

Add constructors to allow different more types of inputs,
including `int`, `double`, and `Fraction`.

Add `sum()` and `negate()` methods to support adding and
subtracting.

Add tests for new methods.

Rename `parseMixedFraction()` to `parseUnsignedMixedFraction()` to
reflect that the input is expected to be unsigned.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add the ability to add and subtract ingredient quantities
commitResults.messageBody:
Add `add()`, `subtract()`, and `isCompatible()` methods.

Add tests for new methods.

Limit largest denominator to 4 for fractions.

Edit `toString()` method of `MixedFraction` to handle pure
fractions.

commitResults.messageTitle: Change implementation of ingredient quantity values
commitResults.messageBody:
Switch from `Integer` and `Double` representation to `BigDecimal`
representation to avoid floating point errors.

Add `getFromBigDecimal()` method to `MixedFraction`.

Fix bugs in `toString()` methods.

Add tests for new methods.

Update old tests.
Add preconditions.

commitResults.messageTitle: Restrict IngredientName validation regex and add tests
commitResults.messageBody:
Restrict the punctuation allowed in an `IngredientName` to dashes,
apostrophes, and percent signs, and restrict the first character
to be alphabets or numbers only.

Add tests to `IngredientNameTest` to test the `toString()` and
`equals()` methods.

commitResults.messageTitle: Construct skeletal structure for Cooking Papa commands
commitResults.messageBody:
Create new subpackages for each category of commands.

Add prefixes used by Cooking Papa to CliSyntax.

Add RecipeAddIngredientCommand.

Add EditRecipeDescription modelled after EditPersonDescriptor in
EditCommand, to edit the ingredients and steps in recipes.

Modify other parts of the code base to support
RecipeAddIngredientCommand, most significantly to Model,
ModelManager, Recipe and UniqueRecipeList.

commitResults.messageBody:
Add tests for addition and subtraction of ingredient quantities
containing fractions.

Fix bug in MixedFraction#toString() that displays whole numbers
as 0.
